question: What fast food restaurant can I find along the way to Aquarium Outfitters Carolina, Wake Forest, NC within 140 kilometers from Raynay Alpaca Farm, Ruffin, NC?
sql:
WITH
    angle AS (SELECT degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-79.503121 36.362766)',4326)::geography, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-78.515805 35.970785)',4326)::geography)) AS value)
SELECT * FROM pois,angle
WHERE amenity = 'fast_food'
AND ST_DWithin(pois.geometry, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-79.503121 36.362766)',4326)::geography, 140000)
AND (degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-79.503121 36.362766)',4326)::geography, pois.geometry)) BETWEEN angle.value - 22.5 AND angle.value + 22.5);
